_xResult.title: Angels Wings Dress
_xResult.shortdesc: Custom made white maxi with golden ribbon on back
_xResult.longdesc:
This custom made oversized maxi is surprisingly stylish and sexy. The front features two side pockets for convenience and the back has a golden ribbon that cascades down the back and adds great visual interest. The sleeves are short and the fabric is made of cotton, so it's super soft and comfortable even if you sweat.

 

Have fun with EUG's custom made designer clothing! For custom made requests regarding sizing, let the designer know using the button below.
